// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
//  stm32u545_devkit.repl — SWM Pramukh / Griha on STM32U545RETxQ
//
//  Platform: STM32U545RE (Cortex-M33, TZEN=0 for RevA).
//  Role:     Master Controller (Pramukh) or Home Controller (Griha),
//            plus the four shim bins (gagan/talab/dhara/nalvar) for
//            the Phase 3.3 brand-name matrix.
//  Power:    Mains-derived 3V3 (Pramukh) or USB-C (Griha) — no charger.
//  Radio:    External LR1121 on SPI1 — same external-module pattern
//            as the STM32G0B1 path.  Phase 6.2.2 inherits the
//            LR1121SpiRadio model from configs/renode/shared/peripherals/lora.
//
//  Inherits the STM32U545 SoC; node-specific peripherals (sensor
//  stubs, relay GPIO) are attached via .resc bindings.
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

using "../../../soc/arm/stm32u545/stm32u545.repl"

// ── LoRa radio (SPI1 @ 0x40013000)
// External LR1121 module on SPI1 (PA5=SCK, PA6=MISO, PA7=MOSI, PA4=NSS).
// stm32u545_devkit.resc unregisters spi1 and loads LR1121SpiRadio.

// ── Ultrasonic / Pressure / Battery
// The U5 ports run the four "non-native" role bins (gagan/talab/dhara/
// nalvar) against the Null sensor HAL today; the .resc still wires the
// shared Python stubs so platform-level smoke tests run identically to
// WLE5 / G0B1.

// ── Relay (Dhara / Nalvar shim bins)
// GPIOB carries relay outputs on the SWM actuator boards.  The .resc
// replaces gpioPortB with the shared relay_gpio stub when the role bin
// is dhara/nalvar.
